118
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:07,932
Just handle it yourself.

119
00:10:08,239 --> 00:10:09,912
Okay, leave it to me!

120
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:20,633
Come. Put this here.

121
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:21,880
And put this one over there.

122
00:10:22,119 --> 00:10:23,119
Here.

123
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,440
Hurry up.

124
00:10:32,359 --> 00:10:34,560
