141
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,592
It's such a good opportunity. Don't walk away.

142
00:11:05,919 --> 00:11:07,552
Take a good look.

143
00:11:10,752 --> 00:11:11,752
Where are you going again?

144
00:11:12,239 --> 00:11:13,239
Give me your hand.

145
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:22,352
How is it? Impressive, isn't it?

146
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:25,232
Luxurious, isn't it?

147
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,232
Surely, you haven't seen a view like this.

148
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,352
You hillbilly.

149
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:33,679
You...

150
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,279
Let's find a place

151
00:11:43,359 --> 00:11:44,359
