152
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,000
I'm going to sit over there.

153
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,080
Where are you going?

154
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,800
I know what you're thinking.

155
00:11:57,880 --> 00:12:00,032
