156
00:12:00,245 --> 00:12:01,546
- No!   - No what?

157
00:12:02,239 --> 00:12:03,352
I know I'm right.

158
00:12:03,599 --> 00:12:04,873
I won't let you have your way.

159
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,960
Come. Go over there.

160
00:12:07,359 --> 00:12:08,359
Sit there.

161
00:12:11,479 --> 00:12:12,479
Go in.

162
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,272
