163
00:12:41,679 --> 00:12:43,712
You're sitting in the back, and you're still staring at him?

164
00:12:44,239 --> 00:12:46,680
Who's staring at him?

165
00:12:46,886 --> 00:12:47,750
I'm just

166
00:12:49,039 --> 00:12:50,039
looking around.

167
00:12:58,719 --> 00:12:59,719
I didn't expect

168
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,073
