175
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:16,760
Yes. What's wrong with that?

176
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,873
When are they getting married?

177
00:13:25,193 --> 00:13:27,426
It sounds like you're looking forward to it.

178
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,320
Yes.

179
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:41,760
Yi Xuan's marriage to the fox clan's crown prince

180
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,273
will definitely be a grand affair.

181
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,393
How could I miss that?

182
00:14:24,599 --> 00:14:26,753
Today is Yi Xuan's birthday.

183
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:29,273
