184
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:30,912
So everyone, please don't be shy.

185
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,313
Eat and drink freely!

186
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:34,552
Thank you, Grandmother Bi Xi.

187
00:14:42,599 --> 00:14:43,325
Sit down.

188
00:14:44,773 --> 00:14:45,773
Hu Zhi Zhi.

189
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,953
Bring up my gift.

190
00:14:49,919 --> 00:14:50,919
Yi Xuan,

191
00:14:51,159 --> 00:14:53,513
we found these rare and exotic plants for you

192
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,753
to help you make elixirs.

193
00:14:56,679 --> 00:14:57,679
Thank you, Grandmother Bi Xi.

194
00:15:06,673 --> 00:15:07,311
Yi Xuan,

195
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,472
this Phoenix Butterfly Gilded Hairpin

196
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:10,993
