202
00:15:36,400 --> 00:15:37,712
A Lovesick Jade Bracelet.

203
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:41,280
Chang Yue,

204
00:15:41,719 --> 00:15:42,792
I like it so much.

205
00:15:58,359 --> 00:15:59,359
Yi Xuan,

206
00:15:59,919 --> 00:16:01,479
- I...   - At this juncture,

207
