00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:11,432
This isn't my home.

284
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,832
If Chang Yue won't ask me to stay,

285
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,393
who will?

286
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:20,553
No one cares about me.

287
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,480
I don't mean that.

288
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:23,633
I don't mean that.

289
00:20:24,319 --> 00:20:26,081
Don't cry. You look hideous when you cry.

290
00:20:26,161 --> 00:20:27,273
So what if I'm ugly?

291
00:20:27,520 --> 00:20:28,800
No one cares even if I'm ugly.

292
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:30,359
Chang Yue doesn't even want me anymore.

293
00:20:30,439 --> 00:20:33,192
He's going to marry another woman.

294
00:20:37,439 --> 00:20:38,999
Hit me! Why aren't you hitting me?

295
00:20:39,079 --> 00:20:41,119
Just punch me a couple of times!

296
00:20:41,199 --> 00:20:42,199
Stop hitting me.

297
00:20:43,319 --> 00:20:44,519
All my life, this is the first time

298
00:20:44,599 --> 00:20:45,673
someone hit me.

299
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:46,920
I have pride too.

300
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,673
Consider this an honor.

301
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:50,432
Are all human women

302
00:20:50,599 --> 00:20:51,793
like this when they are drunk?

303
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:55,352
That's why Chang Yue will not marry you.

304
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,432
This constant stopping and starting...

305
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:19,432
When will we ever get to Suiyue Mountain?

306
00:21:36,119 --> 00:21:37,832
I wonder how much further we have to go.

307
00:21:39,319 --> 00:21:40,680
- Master.   - Give it to them.

308
00:21:40,753 --> 00:21:41,432
Sir.

309
00:21:41,926 --> 00:21:42,926
Thank you.

310
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,592
Qi Lian that old fox

311
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:52,633
insists on resting every other day.

312
00:21:53,199 --> 00:21:55,192
He's clearly stalling for time.

313
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:56,839
And Qi Yuan Bao

314
00:21:56,919 --> 00:21:57,919
is also very strange.

315
00:21:58,273 --> 00:22:00,305
You know Qi Yuan Bao's temper.

316
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:01,873
She's usually mischievous.

317
00:22:02,119 --> 00:22:03,119
How could she possibly

318
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,673
sit so quietly in the carriage now?

319
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:06,793
It's not like her at all.

320
00:22:11,259 --> 00:22:13,252
We can't afford any mistakes in this matter.

321
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:15,192
Ask Su Shen Shen to test her.

322
00:22:15,439 --> 00:22:16,439
Noted.

323
00:22:24,078 --> 00:22:25,078
Shen.

324
00:22:25,199 --> 00:22:26,199
Yun Rong.

325
00:22:32,119 --> 00:22:33,119
Why?

326
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,393
What exactly are you suspecting her of?

327
00:22:37,199 --> 00:22:39,072
Master must have his own reasons.

328
00:22:39,652 --> 00:22:41,793
Shen, let's follow orders.

329
00:22:52,460 --> 00:22:53,460
I'm suffocating.

330
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,119
Cover up! Someone will see you.

331
00:22:56,199 --> 00:22:57,359
No one will see me. Why?

332
00:22:57,439 --> 00:22:58,686
I'm not Yuan Bao so you want me dead?

333
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:00,520
Cover up. It's dangerous!

334
00:23:00,599 --> 00:23:01,599
Don't touch me.

335
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,793
Why are your sister and Yun Rong coming this way?

336
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:10,112
What now? Shen Shen doesn't have freedom either?

337
00:23:16,873 --> 00:23:17,873
What's wrong, Shen?

338
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:19,633
I accidentally twisted my ankle.

339
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:20,949
Does it hurt?

340
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:22,680
It hurts a lot.

341
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:24,112
Your sister twisted her ankle.

342
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:26,280
What do we do?

343
00:23:26,384 --> 00:23:27,206
Quiet.

344
00:23:27,473 --> 00:23:28,945
Miss Qi, Mr. Xue,

345
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:31,399
Shen accidentally twisted her ankle.

346
00:23:31,479 --> 00:23:32,993
Would you mind if she rode in your carriage?

347
00:23:33,153 --> 00:23:33,867
No way!

348
00:23:36,239 --> 00:23:37,993
This is Qishan Sect's best healing ointment.

349
00:23:38,199 --> 00:23:39,199
It works instantly.

350
00:23:39,280 --> 00:23:40,280
Mr. Xue,

351
00:23:40,359 --> 00:23:41,519
Shen's foot injury is serious,

352
00:23:41,599 --> 00:23:43,472
and she can't take a step now.

353
00:23:45,520 --> 00:23:46,520
I'm very concerned about her.

354
00:23:46,599 --> 00:23:47,599
I ask for your understanding.

355
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:48,879
- Oh, no.   - If she comes in,

356
00:23:48,959 --> 00:23:49,959
she'll know it's me.

357
00:23:51,119 --> 00:23:52,119
Miss Su.

358
00:23:55,520 --> 00:23:56,520
Mr. Qi.

359
00:23:56,599 --> 00:23:58,574
Miss Su, the carriage is too small.

360
00:23:58,719 --> 00:24:00,033
Three people can't fit in it.

361
00:24:00,439 --> 00:24:01,439
Mr. Qi,

362
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:03,753
you are usually the most sensible.

363
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:06,232
Why won't you help us

364
00:24:06,599 --> 00:24:08,112
now that I'm injured?

365
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:11,800
You know Yuan Bao.

366
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:12,880
She likes to cause trouble.

367
00:24:13,359 --> 00:24:14,840
If she gets upset,

368
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:15,920
I...

369
00:24:17,359 --> 00:24:18,359
Mr. Qi.

370
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,400
Forgive me then.

371
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:22,779
Pardon my intrusion.

372
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:25,280
Don't come near us.

373
00:24:25,360 --> 00:24:26,680
Yuan Bao and I both have smallpox.

374
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:28,321
It's so itchy! It's a contagious disease.

375
00:24:28,401 --> 00:24:29,633
This is a contagious disease.

376
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:33,232
Don't come near us.

377
00:24:35,119 --> 00:24:36,192
Don't come near us.

378
00:24:40,719 --> 00:24:42,359
It's so itchy. I might die.

379
00:24:43,479 --> 00:24:45,633
At first, I didn't want to tell everyone about this,

380
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:47,312
lest it causes unnecessary problems.

381
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:49,400
But since everyone knows now,

382
00:24:49,700 --> 00:24:50,732
I won't hide it anymore.

383
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:52,273
Worry not.

384
00:24:52,479 --> 00:24:53,680
As long as you don't ride with them,

385
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:55,720
don't stay with them, and don't eat with them,

386
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:57,232
you won't be infected.

387
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:03,273
Yuan Bao, you've also contracted smallpox?

388
00:25:03,471 --> 00:25:05,513
I'm very worried about you. Can I take a look?

389
00:25:10,772 --> 00:25:11,772
Yuan Bao?

390
00:25:12,839 --> 00:25:13,445
Yuan Bao?

391
00:25:14,959 --> 00:25:15,652
Yuan Bao?

392
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:16,818
Yuan Bao.

393
00:25:31,280 --> 00:25:33,393
(That is indeed the scar from the severed spirit root.)

394
00:25:33,959 --> 00:25:35,393
(She is Qi Yuan Bao.)

395
00:25:38,599 --> 00:25:40,312
Miss Su, please go back for now.

396
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:43,560
Shu Ya.

397
00:25:44,479 --> 00:25:46,439
You should go back quickly to avoid being infected.

398
00:25:47,040 --> 00:25:48,040
Right.

399
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:06,153
We made it.

400
00:26:06,560 --> 00:26:07,920
Luckily, Yuan Bao was provident.

401
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,553
She prepared this medicine for me in advance.

402
00:26:10,199 --> 00:26:11,199
She

403
00:26:11,239 --> 00:26:12,480
does have really good foresight.

404
00:26:12,560 --> 00:26:13,760
She told me that Huo Shu Ya

405
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:14,999
would seek the scar on her hand,

406
00:26:15,079 --> 00:26:16,153
and he really did that.

407
00:26:17,560 --> 00:26:18,720
But when can we take the antidote?

408
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:19,800
This is too itchy.

409
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:21,513
Let's just bear with it a little longer.

410
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:23,359
The Huo family really has

411
00:26:23,439 --> 00:26:24,439
ulterior motives towards her.

412
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:26,439
We can't let our efforts be wasted.

413
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:28,119
If I get disfigured because of Yuan Bao,

414
00:26:28,199 --> 00:26:28,732
I'll...

415
00:26:44,239 --> 00:26:45,362
Before

416
00:26:46,023 --> 00:26:48,656
I even have the time to visit Beiming,

417
00:26:49,479 --> 00:26:50,762
and I have to leave already.

418
00:27:00,560 --> 00:27:01,560
Chang Yue.

419
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:04,920
Your soul...

420
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:07,633
Are you really sure you don't want it?

421
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,680
Chang Yue,

422
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:20,232
I'm leaving tomorrow.

423
00:28:23,760 --> 00:28:24,760
Okay.

424
00:28:27,512 --> 00:28:28,512
I wish you

425
00:28:30,119 --> 00:28:31,312
happiness.

426
00:28:34,319 --> 00:28:35,319
Okay.

427
00:28:39,711 --> 00:28:41,453
(Since you don't love me,)

428
00:28:41,614 --> 00:28:43,694
(what's the point of retrieving my soul?)

429
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:49,472
(Since you're going to marry Yi Xuan,)

430
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:52,432
(what's the point of staying here?)

431
00:28:54,184 --> 00:28:55,642
(As for your soul,)

432
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:58,410
(I'll find a way to return it to you.)
